 An exhibition of recent works by Ganesh Haloi will open at Akar Prakar, 6.30 pm. 

 Reality as Fantasy, recent works by various illustrators, at Angan Art Gallery, 4 pm to 8 pm. 

 An exhibition of paintings by members of Bengal Art Society, at Gallery Exposure, 4 pm to 8 pm.

 At Half Mast, an exhibition of paintings and sculptures by Probir Gupta, at Bose Pacia, 11 am to 7 pm.

 Spring-summer collection at 85 Landsdowne (85B Sarat Bose Road), 11 am to 7 pm. 

 An exhibition of accessories at Soumyas Creation, 57/9 Ballygunge Circular Road, 10.30 am to 7 pm. 

 Furniture Show at Ice Skating Rink, 11 am to 8 pm. 




